      "content": "okay i get the analogy. but i am still a bit worried about the \"irreparable\" part. it feels like they are trying to make it sound way scarier than it actually is. like is there a reason they use such dramatic language? does it imply there's some kind of hidden trap in the text that i'm missing?",
